title: Last Week in Slovakia: Slovakia shaken by the murder of an investigative journalist and his fiancee
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary: Investigative reporter Jan Kuciak was found dead in his house in Velka Maca together with his fiancee, Martina Kusnirova. PM Robert Fico offered a million of euros for information that will help clarify the murder.  Local and international community of journalists is shaken.
